  "title": "AB03 - Interior Design Project Executive [ 2 Years Contract ]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Interior Design Project Executive [ 2 Years Contract ]</strong></p><ul><li>Salary: SGD 2,500–3,000 + Bonus</li><li>Working Hours: Monday–Friday: 9 AM–6 PM / Saturday: 9 AM–1 PM</li><li>Working days: 5.5-day work week</li><li>Work Address: Kaki Bukit, Singapore</li><li>Site Travelling Required [ Transport Allowance Provided ]</li></ul><p><em><strong>Job Scope</strong></em></p><ol><li><em><strong>Prepare quotations, material selections & pricing breakdowns</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Present proposals and assist Director in client meetings & deal closures</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Conduct site visits, liaise with contractors, and ensure progress updates</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Draft layout plans, elevations, reflected ceiling plans (RCP), and M&E drawings</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Create 3D visualisations and presentation visuals for client approval</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Produce technical and shop drawings for carpentry & joinery works</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Liaise with workshop, suppliers, clients, and relevant authorities</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Oversee on-site progress, report to Director, and ensure project compliance</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Handle documentation for safety, SFA, PUB, and submission forms when needed</strong></em></li></ol><p><em><strong>Software Required</strong></em></p><ul><li>Provide portfolio / link during application submission, 2 years contract for this post, renewable or convert to permanent based on performance.</li><li><em><strong>AutoCAD (must-have)</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>SketchUp / 3Ds Max / Lumion (for 3D visualisation)</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Photoshop / Canva / PowerPoint (for presentation materials)</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Google Sheets / WhatsApp / Cloud Drive (for communication & documentation)</strong></em></li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
